flowchart TD
    Start([Produk dibuat Admin])

    Start --> InitStock[stock = N<br>stock_reserved = 0<br>total_sold = 0]

    InitStock --> Available[Stok tersedia:<br>stock - stock_reserved]

    Available --> OrderCreated{Customer checkout}

    OrderCreated -->|Pesanan Pending| Reserve[Reserve:<br>stock_reserved += quantity]
    Reserve --> CheckAvailable{"stock - stock_reserved<br>&gt;= 0?"}
    CheckAvailable -->|Tidak| Oversell(["Blokir - oversell prevented"])
    CheckAvailable -->|Ya| PendingState[Status: Pending]

    PendingState --> WhatHappens{Apa yang terjadi?}

    WhatHappens -->|Customer bayar<br>Webhook Midtrans settlement| Settlement[Settlement]
    WhatHappens -->|"&gt; 1 jam<br>Scheduler"| Expiry[Expire]
    WhatHappens -->|Customer batalkan| Cancel[Cancel]
    WhatHappens -->|Webhook Midtrans<br>deny/failure| Fail[Failed]

    Settlement --> DeductReserved[Deduct Reserved:<br>stock -= stock_reserved<br>stock_reserved = 0<br>total_sold += quantity]

    DeductReserved --> PostDeduct[Status: Post-Deduction<br>Processing → ReadyPickup/Shipping → Delivered → Completed]

    PostDeduct --> PostWhat{Apa yang terjadi?}

    PostWhat -->|Webhook Midtrans cancel| PostCancel[Cancel<br>Webhook only]
    PostWhat -->|Webhook Midtrans deny/failure| PostFail[Failed<br>Webhook only]
    PostWhat -->|Admin Refund| RefundPend[RefundPending]

    PostCancel --> RestoreStock[Restore Stock:<br>stock += quantity<br>stock_reserved = 0<br>total_sold -= quantity]
    PostFail --> RestoreStock
    RefundPend --> AutoCancel[Auto-cancel internal]
    AutoCancel --> RestoreStock

    RestoreStock --> Available

    Expiry --> ReleaseReserved[Release Reserved:<br>stock_reserved -= quantity]
    Cancel --> ReleaseReserved
    Fail --> ReleaseReserved

    ReleaseReserved --> Available

    DeductReserved --> Completed{Final?}
    PostWhat -->|Completed| Completed
    Completed --> FinalState([Completed — stok tidak berubah])



